<br>
As to aggro management...it is part of the game, there is no reason why a group should be able to go all out from the get go to kill a mob...at that point why do the fight, just compare numbers and get the exp. The reason people say that the warrior is broken, and in my opinion, does need to be upgraded, is beacuse main tanking is the ONLY thing that they do. They don't solo, they don't cast spells, their DPS is too low, they just don't bring enough chips to the table other then taking damage, which is difficult to do when ya can't hold aggro. And trying to fix this problem by supplying better gear is not the answer.<br>
